query: SELECT workspace_user.workspace_id as "workspace_id: Uuid", role_resource_permissions_type.permission_id as "permission_id: Uuid" FROM role_resource_permissions_type JOIN workspace_user ON workspace_user.role_id = role_resource_permissions_type.role_id WHERE workspace_user.user_id = $1 AND role_resource_permissions_type.permission_type = 'exclude' AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM role_resource_permissions_exclude WHERE role_resource_permissions_exclude.role_id = role_resource_permissions_type.role_id AND role_resource_permissions_exclude.permission_id = role_resource_permissions_type.permission_id );
